		<hr size="1">Question - </P><P>How important is CHA to a bard?  My bard, until recently, is still wearing her newbie armor which makes my bard's total CHA 109.  A high-level guildie gave me 2 pieces of lamb (which I love the graphics on, hehe) and it adds to my HPs, but lowers my CHA.  Should I just keep my original gear or keep the lambient stuff and hope to get a CHA aug in LDoN?  (With the new armor pieces my CHA is lowered to 103.)<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
	</font>
