		<hr size="1">You know how you go to pull a room and there's a mob right behind the door so you get 2 or 3 mobs instead of one?  Eye of Zomm makes it so that never happens.  Go get Phinny... send in the eye, lull all his bodyguards, target him and yoink! <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>Dex is more important at lower levels because most bard skill ups are based on Dex, once your skills are maxed out dex suddenly becomes much less important.</P><P>Int for Mana pool, Cha for a variety of things but most importantly missed notes.  Make a new bard, on the character creation screen highlight Cha and read the description of the stat and how it pertains to Bards.<br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
